com.ibm.team.interop.client.rest
Interface IInteropContent

public interface IInteropContent

Class representing content that has been uploaded to the Jazz repository.

Note that this class is intended for use in representing "attachments" to Jazz items (i.e. work items). Such attachments are considered to be binary files, so there is no provision for specifying the type of line delimiter used.

Since:
0.7
